==English==

===Noun===
'''stalemate'''

#<!--DefA-->''[[Chess]].''  The state in which the player to move is not in check but has no legal moves, resulting in a draw.
#<!--DefB-->Any situation that has no obvious possible movement, but does not involve any personal loss.

